{"tid":1450474,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警狗還眼","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:39:40.000Z","uid":296691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b930fff14ce23f3c753c283d14cc22468e78e876","tid":1450474,"uid":296691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:38:03.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場"},{"pid":"24dc0867b7caf7ae8d18d50e1cd87f0dededc8ed","tid":1450474,"uid":283504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/amiKvLp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FamiKvLp.png&h=5f1d34d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xZJnhqq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZJnhqq.png&h=5f24a051&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kbw0Ow6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKbw0Ow6.png&h=88649463&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hjD21R7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhjD21R7.png&h=b4f53561&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s8GW6iN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs8GW6iN.png&h=5f13979d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Y7SEDO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Y7SEDO.png&h=e29a452b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRQdo5u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRQdo5